      • execute

        protected <T> T execute(org.apache.http.client.protocol.HttpClientContext context,
                        org.apache.http.client.methods.HttpRequestBase request,
                        org.apache.http.client.ResponseHandler<T> responseHandler)
                 throws IOException
        Common method as single entry point responsible fo request execution
        类型参数:
        T - will return raw HttpResponse when responseHandler is null or value reslved using provided ResponseHandler instance
        参数:
        context - clientContext to be used when executing request
        request - Request to execute
        responseHandler - can be null if you need raw HttpResponse or not null response handler for result handling.
        返回:
        value resolved using response handler or raw HttpResponse when responseHandler is null
        抛出:
        IOException
